msgid "‘ye te samaṇabrāhmaṇā cakkhuviññeyyesu rūpesu vītarāgā vītadosā vītamohā, ajjhattaṃ vūpasantacittā, samacariyaṃ caranti kāyena vācāya manasā, evarūpā samaṇabrāhmaṇā sakkātabbā garukātabbā mānetabbā pūjetabbā. "
msgstr "‘There are ascetics and brahmins who are free of greed, hate, and delusion for sights known by the eye, who are peaceful inside, and who conduct themselves well by way of body, speech, and mind. They deserve honor, respect, reverence, and veneration. "

msgctxt "mn150:5.5"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

#. VAR: Mayampi hi → mayaṃ hi (?)
msgctxt "mn150:5.6"
msgid "Mayampi hi cakkhuviññeyyesu rūpesu avītarāgā avītadosā avītamohā, ajjhattaṃ avūpasantacittā, samavisamaṃ carāma kāyena vācāya manasā, tesaṃ no samacariyampi hetaṃ uttari passataṃ. "
msgstr "Because we ourselves are not free of these things, but we see that they have a higher good conduct than us. "

